Description:
On the first folder there is a piece of paper ("Kiste 2 akten 41-53") that doesn't correspond to any of the files in the box

Annotation on the envelope: "Rubens Zweite Heirat und Ausgang der Politik" addressed (inside) to "Herrn Prof. Dr. H. G. Evers Technische Hochschule Institut f. Kunstgeschichte 61 Darmstadt" and dated 20.02.1967

- Extracts from different publications about Rubens' life and political history
- Bibliographic references
- Photos of engraved portraits of dukes, bishops, etc.
- Manuscript (?) of "La République des Provinces-Unies. De 1630 à 1650" by A. Weddington (Paris 1895)
